org.jlab.io.base

Interface DataDescriptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicDataDescriptor, BosDataDescriptor, EvioDataDescriptor, EvioDescriptor, HipoDataDescriptor

    public interface DataDescriptor
    DataDescriptor is the dictionary of a single DataBank object. It consists of a list of Entries by name and integer ID.
